@carbonenginejs/runtime-trinity
================================

Copyright (c) 2026 CarbonEngineJS contributors.

This package contains a JavaScript implementation of CarbonEngine Trinity and
EVE object-graph classes. Current coverage includes controllers, curves, EVE
scene objects and attachments, particles, post-process descriptions, render
jobs, shader and effect graph data, and Trinity core and UI descriptions.

CarbonEngine and Fenris Creations (CCP Games) names, formats, class names, and
class semantics remain the property of their respective owners. These names are
used for interoperability and provenance context. Ported source files identify
their relevant CarbonEngine source paths in file-level provenance comments.

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by CCP Games or
CCP ehf. "EVE Online" and related marks are the property of their respective
owners. No game assets are redistributed in this package.

